item.title: CVE-2021-20741|2024-08-03T17:53:21.842Z -- hitachi -- hitachi%20application%20server%20help
item.description: Cross-site scripting vulnerability in Hitachi Application Server Help (Hitachi Application Server V10 Manual (Windows) version 10-11-01 and earlier and Hitachi Application Server V10 Manual (UNIX) version 10-11-01 and earlier) allows a remote attacker to inject an arbitrary script via unspecified vectors.
